{
  "stem": "894.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I remember there were swamps and leeches, and it was terrible, all night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we got to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And from there, we-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They must have told us where the displaced-persons camp is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we wound up in Bamberg-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] --in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And so they had the UNRRA-- as I remember, the United Nations Relief and something, not relief fund, because it ends with an A.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know what the A stood for.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were running the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I went in, and I volunteered to do-- to work in the office because I spoke some English, and I-- more than spoke-- I read and wrote English.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I thought I could be helpful in communicating between them and the Jewish people that are trickling into the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got care packages as payment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then it took a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we wanted to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sister that was with me met a young man who wanted to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she made the decision to go with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she eventually married him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did not want to go, because I heard that it's very treacherous and very difficult to get to England-- to get to Israel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took you to Cyprus, and all these problems.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
